						               													<description>Who doesn&amp;rsquo;t love building blocks? In this cooperative game 2-5 players try to build four perfect towers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each tower has a different color and is built by playing cards of that color in the right order. The players start the round by choosing the build order. Then, the players try to add cards from their hands to the towers. If they can't, they have to discard a card. Based on the discards of the last player, new cards are divided over the players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play continues until the first player runs out of cards. The final score is based on the height of the created towers. While only limited communication is allowed, the players cooperate to get the highest score.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
